Title: The Abelian Antighost Equation for The Standard Model in the

`t Hooft-Background GaugeComments: Latex2e, 22 pages, no figures, use package amssymb

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B537 (1999) 527-548

In this paper we study the Abelian Anti-ghost equation for the Standard Modelquantized in the 't Hooft-Background gauge. We show that this equation assuresthe non-renormalization of the abelian ghost fields and prevents possibleabelian anomalies.